{
  "stem": "16503.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 367.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'm telling this story because I feel I'm telling it for the ones who are dead, and this is my contribution to the history, which I will be a part of one day.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I'm not crying anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I am sounding very cold maybe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was Christmas, and that was our calendar-- jumping, I am.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And beginning of Christmas-- the beginning of January, we could already hear the-- the front coming closer to us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And again, we could hear the-- the cannons or whatever they were using.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We knew it was the Russians.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That-- we knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't know how they knew it, but they knew it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] all of a sudden, the commandant must have got his orders from the SS.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we were evacuating by foot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] One night, we just were assembled, and we walked.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we joined early in the morning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So we must have got sometime in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We started walking, and then it was early morning because I remember the sight of the people we joined-- well, if you can call it people.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was the death march, which has got its name now.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We didn't know it then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was a line-- a black line of something, which was moving very slowly as far as you could see and as far as you can see behind you.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You continued-- we were sort of pushed into the line-- the ones from-- from Kurzbach.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And you put a foot in front of the other foot, and you kept on going.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "If you fell down-- we are, again, under the SS-- and they are very, very visible.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I mean, they are visible and cruel-- terribly, terribly cruel-- slapping, kicking, shooting.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
